Cases

Case 1. Authorization.
Steps:
1. Open the page with url    https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Enter the valid login into input Username.             Lana230208
3. Enter the valid password into input Password.      TVVtsv230208
4. Click the button “Sign In” and enter the application.
5. Check-up if you are logged in.
       Actual Results:
1. Switched to another page with same url  https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/, but with the different content on it.
2. Welcome message Hello, lana230208, is on the new opened page.
3. The new button “Sign Out” appeared on the top right corner, instead of the button “Sign In”.
4. The button “Sign In” disappeared.

Case 2.     Check-up if the button “Sign Out” is working.
Steps:
1. The page with url    https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
is open with the “Sign Out” button on the top right corner.
2. Move the cursor to the button “Sign Out” and click on it.
3. Check-up if you are logged-out.
       Actual Results:
1. Switched to another page with same url  https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/, but with the different content on it.
2. The new opened page is the main page of the application without any log-in.
3. The inputs for Username and Password appeared.
4. The new button “Sign In” appeared on the top right corner, instead of the button “Sign Out”.
5. The button “Sign Out” disappeared.

Case 3.     New User’s Registration.
Steps:
1. Open the page with url    https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
2. Move the cursor to the input Username in the lower right corner, put the cursor there, and enter the new User’s Name: RobotsWar.
3. Move the cursor to the input Email in the lower right corner, put the cursor there, and enter the new User’s Email:  java@robots.net.
4. Move the cursor to the input Password in the lower right corner, put the cursor there, and enter the new Password: RobotsWar888.
5. Move the cursor to the green button “Sign Up for OurApp” and click on it.
6. Check-up if you are registered.
       Actual Results:
1. Switched to another page with same url  https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/, but with the different content on it.
2. Welcome message Hello, robotswar, is on the new opened page.
3. The new button “Sign Out” appeared on the top right corner, instead of the button “Sign In”.
4. The button “Sign In” disappeared.

Case 4.     Check-up if the button “Create Post” is working.
Steps:
1. The page with url    https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/ is open with the “Sign Out” button on the top right corner and with the text “Hello robotswar, your feed is empty.”
2. Move the cursor to the button “Create Post” and click on it.
3. Now you are redirected to another page with the different url  https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/create-post
4. Create the new post, using 3 empty fields for input by filling them in:
   4.1. Move the cursor to the input Title and enter any Title of the post: RobotsWar
   4.2. Move the cursor to the input BodyContent and enter any Title of the post: RobotsWar was very difficult task.
   4.3. Mark tick or ignore the input if it is a unique post or not. We mark as unique “tick”.
   4.4. Move the cursor to the input Select value and select one of the three options. Let’s select “Private message”
5. Move the cursor to the blue button “Save New Post” and click on it.
6. Check-up if the button “Create Post” is working.
       Actual Results:
1. Switched to another page with different url   https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/post/60f1614919ae4c00045668f9 , and with the different content on it.
2. The message “New post successfully created”, appeared on the new opened page.
3. The content of the new post is on this page with all the details when it was posted and who posted it: “Posted by robotswar on 7/16/2021”
4. In the lower right corner,  two buttons “Edit” and “Delete”.
5. The newly created post has the ID, mentioned in url    post/60f1614919ae4c00045668f9.

Case 5.     Check-up if the option “Search” is working.
Steps:
1. The page with url    https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/ is open with the “Sign Out” button on the top right corner and with the text “Hello lana230208, your feed is empty.”
2. Move the cursor to the search icon on the top of menu “Seacrh” and click on it.
3. Now you are redirected to another page with the same url  https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/, but with the different content with the search input “What are you interested in?”
4. Input the text from the previous test4 “robotswar” , and we can see in pop-up line, that 1 item found.
5. Move the cursor to the found post RobotsWar and click on it.
6. Check-up if the option “Search” is working.
       Actual Results:
1. Switched to another page with different url   https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/post/60f1614919ae4c00045668f9 , and with the different content on it.
2. The message “This post was written for one person”, appeared on the new opened page.
3. The content of the new post is on this page with all the details when it was posted and who posted it: “Posted by robotswar on 7/16/2021”.
4. The newly created post has the ID, mentioned in url    post/60f1614919ae4c00045668f9.


